column1: Regular traffic reports will resume Thursday June 21 at 4:00 p.m.

column4: Georgetown Rd between Berea Rd and Iron Works Pike
column5: Roadway shutdown in both directions.  Injury collision reportedly involving three vehicles and a pedestrian.  The incident location is just north of Berea Rd.

column4: UPDATE 1:32 p.m. - Clear.  Roadway now open.
